==Critical reception==
[[The Hindu]] wrote, "''Kappal'' fulfils its only purpose&nbsp;— to be funny...here’s actor Vaibhav’s big breakthrough as a solo hero. This ''Kappal'' sails strong for the most part".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/features/cinema/cinema-reviews/review-this-kappal-doesnt-sink/article6725209.ece|title=This Kappal doesn’t sink|author=Sudhir Srinivasan|work=The Hindu}}</ref> [[Sify]] called ''Kappal'' a "watchable fun ride with witty dialogues and good writing".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sify.com/movies/kappal-review-tamil-15058792.html|title=Review : Kappal|work=Sify}}</ref> [[Rediff]] gave the film 2.5 stars out of 5 and wrote, "There may be flaws, but there is no denying that Karthik G Krish’s ''Kappal'' is thoroughly entertaining. But do remember to leave your thinking cap at home".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/review-kappal-is-a-mindless-comedy-south/20141229.htm|title=Review: Kappal is a mindless comedy|date=29 December 2014|work=Rediff}}</ref> [[The Times of India]] gave 3 stars out of 5 and wrote, "Karthik G Krish, is not after heavy philosophy but entertainment. So, he constructs the film as a comedy that is often silly, at times offensive but overall funny".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/tamil/movie-reviews/Kappal/movie-review/45653462.cms|title=Kappal Movie Review|work=The Times of India}}</ref> silverscreen.in wrote, "''Kappal'' is like that old joke, which only gets better with age. It also sustains the good spirit that the riotous pattimandram (debate talk show) of [[Solomon Pappaiah]] offers on festive mornings".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://silverscreen.in/reviews/kappal-review-smooth-sailing/|title=Kappal Review: Smooth Sailing|work=Silverscreen.in}}</ref> [[The New Indian Express]] wrote, "Directed by a debutant, it’s meant to be a total comic entertainer. But then it depends on each one’s perception of what they feel are genuine comic moments"...going on to add that the film was "comedy probably targeted at the lowest common denominator in the audience".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/tamil/Comedy-Aimed-at-Lowest-Common-Denominator/2014/12/28/article2591741.ece|title=Comedy Aimed at Lowest Common Denominator|work=The New Indian Express}}</ref>

==Box office==
The film is reported to have grossed around {{INRConvert|5.7|c}} in TN and {{INRConvert|2|c}} from Rest of India and Overseas.<ref>[http://www.behindwoods.com/tamil-movies-cinema-news-14/kappal-sailing-strong-towards-victory.html "Kappal - Sailing strong" ] 30 December 2014. Retrieved 30 December 2014.</ref> The film collected {{INRConvert|12|c}} in its full run.

